version_description: These are the chords for Taylor Swift's new song "Gorgeous" from her album "reputation".
The chords for Taylor Swift’s new song, Gorgeous.
This version is in the key of C and is easy to play along with the song. Enjoy :).
I do think mine is much easier to learn than the rest and have substantial differences from the others in playing the chorus.
I think it's more correctly and easier to play
